For UI work, prioritize:
- accessible contrast and semantics
- strong typography and spacing rhythm
- responsive layout integrity
- consistent component/system patterns

Avoid low-contrast text, noisy visual layering, and inconsistent spacing.

Reference: https://github.com/pbakaus/impeccable
